+## Fork Notice
+
+This repository is a personal fork of [`jesseduffield/lazygit`](https://github.com/jesseduffield/lazygit) maintained at [`endalk200/lazygit`](https://github.com/endalk200/lazygit).
+
+The goal is to stay close to upstream and regularly pull in upstream improvements while keeping a small set of fork-specific patches.
+
+Huge thanks to Jesse Duffield and all lazygit contributors for the original project.
+
+## What Is Different From Upstream
+
+- AI-assisted commit message generation integrated into the commit message flow.
+- The AI action is wired to an external command so it stays tool-agnostic.
+- The intended companion CLI is `better-commit`, published as:
+  - npm package: `@better-tools/commit-message`
+  - Homebrew package in `endalk200/homebrew-tap`
+
+## Install And Run This Fork
+
+1. Install this fork from Homebrew tap:
+
+```bash
+brew tap endalk200/homebrew-tap
+brew install lazygit-endalk
+brew link --overwrite lazygit-endalk
+```
+
+2. Install the companion AI CLI:
+
+```bash
+npm install -g @better-tools/commit-message
+```
+
+3. Configure lazygit to use the CLI:
+
+```yaml
+git:
+  commit:
+    aiCommitMessage:
+      command: "better-commit"
+```
+
+4. Run:
+
+```bash
+lazygit
+```
+
